Que 31) What is ActivatedRoute?
-------------------------------
ActivatedRoute is used to get data from the URL.
Example: If URL has ID â†’ /user/5
We can read 5 using ActivatedRoute.
âœ… Example Route:
{ path: 'user/:id', component: UserComponent }
âœ… In Component:
