âœ… Why use Functional Components?
âœ” Simple and clean code
âœ” Easy to test
âœ” Better performance for small components
âœ” Good for reusable UI parts
ğŸ¯ When should you use them?
Use functional components when:
You only need to display data
There is no complex logic
You are creating small reusable UI parts (like buttons, cards, labels)
ğŸ“Œ Example in Simple Words
Imagine a component that only shows a user name:
Input â†’ name
Output â†’ Display "Hello, Mahesh"
It doesnâ€™t need heavy logic â€” so a functional component is perfect.
ğŸ“Œ In One Line
